WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.629
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:04.630
doing today? Well, praise the Lord. I

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:07.510
really appreciate you joining me. I

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:10.390
was sent some articles about

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.070
what I saw

00:00:12.070 --> 00:00:12.080
regarding

00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:15.030
the cyber attacks, and people

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:16.870
are sending me stuff saying, 'Brandon,

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:18.390
we started looking into what you were

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:21.109
talking about and the United States is

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:26.150
using Windows 95 with the

00:00:26.150 --> 00:00:26.160
FAA.'And

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.710
I was like, 'Surely

00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:28.720
not.'30-year-old

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:33.510
software. Like, really? I mean, so Braden

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:35.030
started

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.030
researching and making sure before I

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.389
talk about it, you know, because you don't

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:39.670
want to look

00:00:39.680 --> 00:00:41.190
off. You want to make sure it's

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:45.190
right. They are using 1995 floppy disks, and

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.110
they're trying to update it, and

00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:48.069
they're saying it's going to take at

00:00:48.079 --> 00:00:51.270
least four years because of how vast

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:54.150
this system is and all the computers, and

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:55.750
it's going to cost billions

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:58.229
of dollars to renew the infrastructure

00:00:58.239 --> 00:01:01.189
of the FAA computer systems.

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:04.390
Billions is what they're saying. So all

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.550
that I was talking about and what

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.870
the Lord showed me in my prayer time is

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:11.350
legit. Obviously, when you're using

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:15.109
software from 1995, and it's 30-year-old

00:01:15.119 --> 00:01:16.950
software, and you're using computers with

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:18.950
floppy disks, I mean, this is a major

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:21.109
deal. We're going into a new industrial

00:01:21.119 --> 00:01:25.109
revolution with 1995 software, with AI

00:01:25.119 --> 00:01:27.670
technology using quantum computers, and

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:31.910
we have 1995 software with AI. So

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:34.630
obviously, when you have other countries

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:37.670
being able to tap into the AI and hack

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:40.069
into our infrastructure, it's probably not

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:41.670
going to be that hard.

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.429
I wonder if they're using

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:46.870
dial-up, you know? I mean,

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:48.950
and it's like, no,

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:51.030
this is not cool.

00:01:51.030 --> 00:01:51.040
And

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:52.469
they're saying it could take up to four

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.789
years, so that's all of President

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:58.630
Trump's term, clear up past it. I mean,

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.789
that's a major deal. So,

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:03.429
that was part of it. Then,

00:02:03.439 --> 00:02:06.630
right after that, we see the airlines

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:09.669
that the Lord spoke to me about. One

00:02:09.669 --> 00:02:09.679
was

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:11.190
on fire and had to do

00:02:11.190 --> 00:02:11.200
an

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.630
emergency landing in the middle of the

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:14.630
air. This is another sign of something

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.150
that the Lord's trying to warn everybody

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.710
about. Right after I give you the word,

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:20.869
not even 24 hours later, there's a

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:22.390
plane and it's caught fire in the

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:23.589
middle of the air, and it has to do an

00:02:23.599 --> 00:02:25.750
emergency landing, and you can see people

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:27.190
filming it and it's burning and doing

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:29.589
all this stuff. And I thought, 'Lord,

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:31.030
you're speaking so loud trying to warn

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:33.350
your people to pray.'You know, like I

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:35.430
said, God has not called us to fear; He

00:02:35.430 --> 00:02:35.440
has

00:02:35.440 --> 00:02:37.589
called us to pray. But He's warning

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:40.390
us about things, telling us, 'Look,

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.309
look, look, there's a problem here.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:44.390
There's a problem there.'And when I saw

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:46.790
the plane falling out of the sky, you

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:49.030
know, I don't know what caused that. I

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:51.750
was assuming cyber attacks, but how

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:53.910
could you get to the plane and turn it

00:02:53.920 --> 00:02:55.910
off? I have no idea. All I know

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:58.309
is I saw a plane; its dash went

00:02:58.319 --> 00:03:00.790
completely blank and it fell, and it

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:02.949
was very dangerous.

00:03:02.959 --> 00:03:04.229
I could tell you where it

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:06.390
was leaving from. It was leaving

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:09.830
from the central part of America and

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:13.509
it was going northeast. It was going

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:15.830
northeast to like the Boston area, and this

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.750
was a major flight, and it was halfway

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:19.750
there and it went down. I can tell you

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:21.110
that's what it looked like.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:22.790
Now, is that going to be every

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:25.190
plane? And is that

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:26.710
just something that the Lord's trying to

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.710
show us, is what I'm trying to say, or is

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:30.630
that the exact flight?

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.390
Because sometimes He's

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:34.390
just showing me an example of something

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:36.149
to pray about and saying, 'Hey, just

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:37.430
letting you know the flights.'Just kind

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.750
of like people are saying about the

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.869
boat, and they're trying to figure out,

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:42.630
and they have trackers on all the boats.

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:44.390
So, you're sending me the trackers of

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:47.350
all the red decks with all the

00:03:47.350 --> 00:03:47.360
black-bottom

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.030
boats with the white thing,

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:50.550
and they're sending stuff, saying 'we got to

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.990
track this boat, and this is where it's

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.509
at.'Now

00:03:53.519 --> 00:03:55.830
folks, I'm going to tell you, whenever I

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:59.110
saw this boat, it was leaving Africa. It

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.869
was leaving that area

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:03.030
over there, and it

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:07.030
was headed this way. So, the

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:07.040
crew—I've

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:08.309
told you all about that. I don't

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:09.670
need to rehearse all that, but it was

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:12.470
coming out of

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:12.480
the

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:15.270
Europe area, Africa, all that area.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:17.030
That's all I remember—seeing Africa in a

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:18.469
distance, and it was coming out of that

00:04:18.479 --> 00:04:21.189
area. And number three, about

00:04:21.189 --> 00:04:21.199
what

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:22.390
people wanted to know about the

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:24.790
buildings and the electric outages: I

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:27.189
saw cyber attacks coming upon our

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:29.189
electric grid, that it was very

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:32.390
vulnerable. And I saw it was a major city,

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:35.270
and I saw it was New York, and

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.189
it was completely dark. And that's

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:39.030
whenever I told my son they were trying

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:41.749
to bring in generators to keep people

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:45.030
from looting and rioting,

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:46.950
stealing everything because it was so

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:49.270
dark in the city. And I could

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:50.950
remember seeing those big spotlights

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:53.189
running on generators, trying to keep

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:55.830
sections of the city lit up so that the

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:57.350
police and the law enforcement could

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.749
keep law and order in that area when the

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:01.990
electricity was off. But I remember it

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:05.189
was very hot outside. And I told Braden,

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:07.189
I even saw the emergency power on

00:05:07.199 --> 00:05:09.189
hospitals coming on. So they were trying

00:05:09.199 --> 00:05:11.830
to keep people alive in hospitals, but

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:13.430
it was a dimmer light; it wasn't as

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:15.110
bright as normal, like

00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:15.120
the hospital

00:05:15.120 --> 00:05:16.629
all lit up—it was

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:19.830
like backup power. And so, you know,

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:21.350
I see these things, but I thought it was

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:22.790
interesting in this vision, whenever I

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.230
was praying and the Lord was showing me

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:25.990
that the light was shining on the

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.390
buildings, trying to cause a mirror

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:30.790
effect so that it would glow more

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:32.070
instead of just having it shoot

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:33.590
straight up in the air. It was trying to

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.189
shine on the buildings to cause

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:36.870
light down below, like blocking the light

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:38.870
from just going straight up is what it

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.950
would look like in the vision. So,

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:43.270
that's part of what I saw too. So, you

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:45.270
know, I see all these things and the

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.590
Lord tells us what to pray about.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:50.070
I believe there's a lot of

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:53.510
things that we can stop in prayer,

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:55.830
as everybody knows

00:05:55.830 --> 00:05:55.840
who

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:57.430
is a prayer warrior. Hey, and by

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:59.749
the way, whoever sent me these hankies

00:05:59.749 --> 00:05:59.759
because

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:02.469
I was using the Kleenex

00:06:02.479 --> 00:06:05.830
there, she embroidered my last name

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:07.670
on it. And I thought it was really nice

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:10.150
of the sister to do that. You know,

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.629
it's too pretty to blow your nose in. I

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:13.830
was like, 'Hey, you know, somebody

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:15.510
writes your name on it.'I don't blow my

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.590
nose in it, but it's really pretty. I

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:19.510
appreciate it. You know, that people

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:21.270
take the time to do stuff like that. I

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:22.550
don't know if you had a machine do

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:23.670
that or whatever, but I thought it was

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:25.670
kind of cool. The other thing: praying

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:27.990
over our water supply, praying over

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.430
because, you know, I've told you about

00:06:29.440 --> 00:06:32.150
the water supply. Oh, and

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:34.469
then somebody sent me a thing about

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:38.629
they found an 80-mile-wide asteroid,

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:40.550
and it's by Neptune or something, and

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.150
they were freaking out about that

00:06:42.150 --> 00:06:42.160
because

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:44.390
Fox News said it was, and they

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.990
said it was—I don't know if it's coming

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.909
this way or not, but I'm telling

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:50.390
you, I get so much now from people

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:52.309
that are into articles, and they send it

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:54.309
to Diana and she goes,

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:55.670
'Brandon, I think you should see

00:06:55.670 --> 00:06:55.680
this.'And

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:57.590
I'm like, 'Wow, I'm getting a lot of

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:00.390
cool stuff.'So, there's

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:02.870
an asteroid that is 80 miles wide. This thing

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:05.350
is massive. I mean, that's a huge

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.749
piece of ice or rock or whatever it is

00:07:07.759 --> 00:07:10.230
that's flying around out there. Then

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:12.790
I see an article from Fox News saying

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:15.110
that Trump and Bibi have agreed on a

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:17.430
two-state solution. And that was one of

00:07:17.440 --> 00:07:20.070
the things from the Abraham Accords. And

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:21.670
they were saying how they were wanting

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:23.430
to make a two-state solution; they were

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:25.670
agreeing upon it. And I've already told

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:28.390
you all: if they do this

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:32.390
two-state solution, three days later,

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:34.550
the New Madrid fault line will be split

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:36.710
in half, and America will be divided in

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:39.110
half. If you want to watch that, that

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:41.589
video is down below. I told you all when

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.150
this happens, I saw great big Chinook

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:48.230
helicopters flying from the west to

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:50.710
the central part of America. They had

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:52.629
supplies. They were trying. It sounded

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:55.110
like the earth was shaking. They had so

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.950
many helicopters trying to bring

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:59.350
supplies from the west to the central

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:01.110
part where the United States was

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.869
divided. This is whenever I told you I

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:05.189
saw the lion's face and I thought,

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:07.110
"What is this lion's face?"And it was

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:09.110
carved into a side of a building and I

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:11.510
warned everybody. I saw

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:11.520
tumbleweeds

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:14.469
going down Wall Street. I saw a side

00:08:14.469 --> 00:08:14.479
of the building

00:08:14.479 --> 00:08:16.790
and I saw

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:18.950
the lion,

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:20.550
and the Lord spoke to me. He

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.070
said, "Look at the lion on the side of

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:23.350
the building."But I didn't know what

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.110
building it was, but it is the New York

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:27.510
Stock Exchange. That's what this

00:08:27.520 --> 00:08:28.950
building is. And the Lord warned me

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:31.990
about it. And he told me, "If you divide

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.670
Jerusalem, if they do a two-state

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:35.350
solution and they do this, I'm going to

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:37.589
divide

00:08:37.589 --> 00:08:37.599
America."And

00:08:37.599 --> 00:08:39.430
I saw it split down the middle. I

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:42.389
saw all the bridges that were going

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:44.550
from west to east that were completely

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:47.750
destroyed on the Mississippi River.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:49.350
I saw it was the most

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.350
devastating. And I saw from

00:08:51.350 --> 00:08:51.360
Texarkana

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:53.190
to Tulsa, Oklahoma, I saw over

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:56.230
1,800 people die. And the massive

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:58.470
building that's at OU was split down the

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:01.829
middle. The big skyscraper look, you

00:09:01.839 --> 00:09:04.150
know, that big hospital-looking building

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:05.910
was split down the middle

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.430
when this earthquake takes place. I saw

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:09.509
it completely. Half of the building was

00:09:09.509 --> 00:09:09.519
broken

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:10.870
off at the top and it broke down,

00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:12.150
and all that was laying on the ground,

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:16.310
and I remember it was on fire.

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:18.870
And then I saw all the houses that

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:20.550
were built on cinder blocks were

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:23.509
completely leveled.

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:25.590
Houses that were on a foundation were

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:27.509
better, but the people who had houses on

00:09:27.519 --> 00:09:28.949
cinder blocks, they completely were

00:09:28.959 --> 00:09:31.910
gone. And I saw the New Madrid; there

00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:31.920
were

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:33.910
thousands of people that

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:36.550
passed away from this event that takes

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:39.110
place. And that's why I've always told

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:41.990
people, we must not divide Jerusalem

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:47.269
ever. For when we do, three days after—I want

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:48.870
you to hear me, that's how strong this

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:51.990
word was. He said that the

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:56.470
Liberty Bell—I saw the bell ringing.

00:09:56.480 --> 00:10:00.630
I saw bells, old cast iron bells ringing

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:03.829
when this happens.

00:10:03.839 --> 00:10:06.470
Three days after it's divided and it's

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:09.030
agreed upon. We have three days and

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.350
he'll divide America. I'm talking

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.110
straight down the middle. So, that's one

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:15.030
thing you need to know. We must pray

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:17.030
that this does not take place. It's

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:18.790
very, very important. This is the

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:20.550
article saying that they want to make a

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:23.670
two-state solution. And it's on multiple

00:10:23.680 --> 00:10:25.350
Abraham Accords and all these

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:26.550
different things, these peace agreements.

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:26.560
They

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:28.069
want to do all this, but it's on

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:30.550
